works.description: The whole world is celebrating the 50th anniversary of the first-ever manned space flight, by Soviet Cosmonaut Yuri Alekseyevich Gagarin, this month. Yesterday, we did a roundup of the 10 awesome items space enthusiasts can’t afford to miss from the Bonhams’ upcoming Space History Sale and today, we have picked the best of space inspired wristwatches that are sure to impress the space enthusiasts and lovers of fine watchmaking alike. Hit the jump to see them all
